Test results related to the first bird flu case detected in a human suggested that the main mode of influenza A H5N1 virus transmission was bird-to-human, it was known here Saturday.
The Central Government and relevant departments in Guangdong Province have tightened quarantine controls and offered active assistance to Hong Kong in the battle against bird flu, according to Foreign Ministry spokesman Tang Guoqiang.
The virus, known to cause "bird influenza" in chickens, has been transferred to human beings in Hong Kong The virus is believed to be transmitted through direct contact with poultry or from contact with bird droppings.
